

{"id":6794,"date":"2024-06-10T10:03:52","date_gmt":"2024-06-10T03:03:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/?p=6794"},"modified":"2024-06-10T10:03:52","modified_gmt":"2024-06-10T03:03:52","slug":"3-bai-tap-don-gian-voi-may-chay-bo-cho-nguoi-moi-bat-dau","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/3-bai-tap-don-gian-voi-may-chay-bo-cho-nguoi-moi-bat-dau\/","title":{"rendered":"3 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6795 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2084-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, b\u00e0i t\u1eadp\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1703\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2084-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2084-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2084-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2084-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2084-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/TNG2084-2048x1363.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n tim m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft m\u01b0a hay n\u1eafng, m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i t\u1ed1i \u0111a, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i ch\u1ea1y b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9, t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>M\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/b><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 l\u00e0 g\u00ec, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nhanh h\u01a1n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1ed7i m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c nhau m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u1ec1 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1eabn gi\u1ed1ng nhau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eang v\u00e0 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang khi ch\u1ea1y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. N\u1eafm v\u1eefng nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a l\u1ee3i \u00edch t\u1eeb m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The New Gym th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp, ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng khu v\u1ef1c luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y m\u00f3c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb. The New Gym khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch b\u1ea1n tham gia bu\u1ed5i gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a The New Gym lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>3 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1edbi m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u<\/b><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>1. \u0110i b\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c, h\u00e3y gi\u1eef cho vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 15-20 ph\u00fat \u0111i b\u1ed9 nghi\u00eang, 1-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n. Khi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c \u1edf m\u1ee9c v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i (8-10) v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 4-5 km\/h. C\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u00e1nh c\u1ea7m tay v\u1ecbn n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n, h\u00e3y nghi\u00eang ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a h\u00f3a l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ed1c.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>2. Ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 d\u1ed1c<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nhanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eang v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i (5-7) v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 trong kho\u1ea3ng 9-11 km\/h. Khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t 200m, h\u00e3y gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eang \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c trong 1-3 ph\u00fat. L\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 l\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ghi l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 200m v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n theo th\u1eddi gian.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><b>3. Ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat\u00a0<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ean 15 km\/h trong 30 gi\u00e2y.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat, nh\u1ea3y kh\u1ecfi \u0111ai m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u1edf hai b\u00ean trong 30 gi\u00e2y.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i 10 l\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, h\u00e3y ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3m th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 hay b\u1ea1n \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe tim m\u1ea1ch b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi, The New Gym \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 cho b\u1ea1n. H\u00e3y th\u1eed c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n ho\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a The New Gym \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The New Gym &#8211; Gym cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/span><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Email: cskh@thenewgym.vn<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Hotline: 1900 63 69 20<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&#8211; Facebook: The New Gym<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Zalo OA: <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/zalo.me\/thenewgym\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/zalo.me\/thenewgym<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">